cu.explanation_en: Setting local_s_portd to 70000 (exceeds valid port range) will cause socket binding failure and F1 data interface error.

du.explanation_en: Setting local_n_address to null will cause missing IP address and front-haul interface binding failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 local_n_address 設定為 null 會導致 IP 地址缺失並造成前傳介面綁定失敗。
